3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The proposed port system may involve the use of computer vision techniques for drone detection and tracking during landing and takeoff. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the technical specifications and performance metrics of the proposed port system, which falls under the domain of systems and control engineering. 
5. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper discusses the landing and takeoff of multiple drones, which can be considered as a multi-agent system.
